PRIVATE DINING IN WASHINGTON, DC
With multiple private spaces available, guests can find the perfect room for their next occasion at any of our Pisco y Nazca locations. Gatherings of all sizes ranging from corporate events, graduations, and bridal showers are welcome to enjoy our intimate dining rooms – the ideal setting for a memorable experience. Customized prix fixe menus, cocktail reception menus, and drink packages are available along with a dedicated event coordinator who will ensure your event is a success.
THE PERFECT PLACE FOR YOUR GATHERINGS
Let our professional event coordinator help you plan your next event. From the right menu to the perfect space, we’ll make sure no detail goes overlooked.
State of the art sound systems
HD Projection screen
Accommodating up to 2 rooms each of 20 or 40 guests total

Floor plans are upon request.
